divs: Sighting Detailsi was sitting in my backyard enjoying my last day of summer when my buddy pointed out a orb really low in the sky the orb was moving extremely fast with one solid light heading southeast and then fading out miles ahead . I have been investigating for about 4 years now but never witnessed one in person and i must say it defiantly makes you feel strange.
